<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Content on 忍ばない怠惰テックノート</title><link>/series/content/</link><description>Recent content in Content on 忍ばない怠惰テックノート</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>ja</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 23:00:00 -0300</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/series/content/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Static Content</title><link>/features/static-content/</link><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 23:00:00 -0300</pubDate><guid>/features/static-content/</guid><description>&lt;p>Some of the static content on the site, like the home greetings and side pane content, can be defined in the file at &lt;code>data/rtwt/content.yaml&lt;/code>. The structure to do so is as follows:&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Note: It&amp;rsquo;s possible to use file formats other than YAML, but the key structure must remain the same!&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">home&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">image&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;images/greetings.jpg&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">greetings&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;A Hugo Theme for Bloggers!&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">text&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;The definitive, configurable, customizable, old fashioned rusty coloured theme for web writers and readers.&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">side&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">home&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> - &lt;span style="color:#f92672">content&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;Oh, and did I mention it has support for static side pane content? Cool, right?&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> - &lt;span style="color:#f92672">title&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;Media Support&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">content&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;Side content can have images!&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">imagePath&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;images/hugo.svg&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">imageHref&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;https://gohugo.io&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">imageWidth&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;100%&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Didn&amp;rsquo;t find a value you&amp;rsquo;re looking for? Check the &lt;a href="https://github.com/math-queiroz/rusty-typewriter">repository&lt;/a> for the given file (which may be updated with it), or create a new feature request!&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>